cdata.name: ZeitCoin
cdata.desc:
Zeitcoin is a cryptocurrency that allows insant peer-to-peer payments to anyone, withou the oversight of any central authority. Zeitcoin is a charity and activism driven coin. ZEIT uses a sustainable PoS algorithm with dynamic staking rewards:

25% during the first year

20%during the secondyear

15%during the thirdyear

5% until all coins have been mined
